{"tid":495791,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"切勿過份相信自己既理性，會害死你","createTime":"2017-12-11T04:57:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T17:24:45.000Z","uid":123335,"like":14,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"8d95b53659cbdcd2e677b4fa83b9933fc7b39061","tid":495791,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T04:57:04.000Z","msg":"雖然大家會發覺呢個世界都好make sense <br />\n絕大部份都可以用理性去解讀, 去理解, 甚至係預測 <br />\n似乎理性, logic 就係一種可信程度極高既工具<br />\n<br />\n但要小心，切勿過份相信自己既理性<br />\n會害死你<br />\n<br />\n大家可能想問，吓，信理性都唔可靠？<br />\n答案：係 <br />\n<br />\n因為你地當下既理性，唔係以全知既角度去分析<br />\n往往都係以lack of data 下既姿態去使用理性<br />\n呢個情況下, 當刻伴隨住自己既主觀既情緒, 會對理性分析有決定性既影響<br />\n<br />\n相信大家都聽過：「凡事都有兩面，有兩睇」<br />\n就黎聖誕節就舉個例關於溝女3次都失敗<br />\ne.g. 正面情緒(+理性) : 哦, 唔緊要, \b再試第4個target , 相信之前果d 唔夾姐<br />\n負面情緒(+理性): 唉, 我條件太差, 冇米8, 唔靚仔, 唔會再溝到女架啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n理性係絕對有參考價值<br />\n但唔好過份相信自己當下既理性<br />\n講野make sense 唔代表你就係真理 <br />\n因為人類做唔到全知既理性分析 <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打明我講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a274c366771e1f0453d7e419dce60f8d6858816","tid":495791,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:05:49.000Z","msg":"nobody?"},{"pid":"c1bf9ee4062f5ef3bbe8894c52447a65559c4124","tid":495791,"uid":37869,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:06:46.000Z","msg":"理性唔可靠<br />\n但理性係人類做決定時唯一可以依賴又較可靠的野<br />\n唔相信理性 仲可以相信乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以為睇到最後會見到你話要相信神"},{"pid":"a86db7b39ea6701278e1b74742dd213b0f055862","tid":495791,"uid":134504,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:07:57.000Z","msg":"山係石頭，海係水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9678e02f1da98e4b51ff6277038d0db540365d50","tid":495791,"uid":116289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:08:53.000Z","msg":"你老母係女人"},{"pid":"52d823c259d0d5dbe03dc7a6be23ea1c42d28865","tid":495791,"uid":150775,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:09:15.000Z","msg":"冇女講咁多野想逃避現實姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa57bf2617512e5ee5ceaed61275bda83c93e05","tid":495791,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:10:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>理性唔可靠<br />\n但理性係人類做決定時唯一可以依賴又較可靠的野<br />\n唔相信理性 仲可以相信乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以為睇到最後會見到你話要相信神</blockquote><br />\n主要想講當刻既理性唔可靠<br />\n建議做重要決定時，俾多D時間自己<br />\n會更加易接近做到個真正理性既決定"},{"pid":"caff57ba91d6f3938ec91defe005dbd21779c813","tid":495791,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:12:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Ego Kills<br />\n自我會殺死你</span></span>"},{"pid":"0d360b78ac2445eb4eeaaf4a5b3bf1e4cf5f2e9d","tid":495791,"uid":53218,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:16:59.000Z","msg":"用個扭曲左既思想仲點叫理性"},{"pid":"38cb025ca36f531df8f261ac3a3f97327020c02b","tid":495791,"uid":150611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:18:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b02abae9131f4765e9b5118a60bcd6ee615de4e","tid":495791,"uid":74278,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:19:45.000Z","msg":"你究竟知唔知咩叫理性"},{"pid":"24023755e078c2d7adaf5044390d93c260d45870","tid":495791,"uid":51129,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:21:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正面情緒(+理性) : 哦, 唔緊要, \b再試第4個target , 相信之前果d 唔夾姐</blockquote><br />\n成個論證得兩個字「相信」，見唔到理性喺邊喎"},{"pid":"36f89ca3a55ca7cbadce35f55ca1bc9d616e00f3","tid":495791,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:31:23.000Z","msg":"樓主終於都明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主老母倍感安慰"},{"pid":"919b2d8c810eaabf9181a23f893d4b8eae068b89","tid":495791,"uid":136590,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:31:35.000Z","msg":"Thinking, Fast and Slow<br />\n睇過呢本書嘅人就會知人絕對唔係理性嘅生物<br />\n啲bias多到嚇死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f9f6e291c8625814b668af688ca28ca4aa62b3","tid":495791,"uid":60120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:43:28.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪想講<br />\n唔夠資訊，推理唔到<br />\n所以用唔完整嘅推理黎做決定會好危險?"},{"pid":"0f924af751fe7b68a056788dbaabe79d07b2c673","tid":495791,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:48:10.000Z","msg":"理性唔可靠，是事實。<br />\n但感性和情感更不可靠，又係事實。"},{"pid":"7fc85ad37830c88343dc8350b40e3f44734a78dc","tid":495791,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:51:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇女講咁多野想逃避現實姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n媾女四寶：樣、錢、口才、工作能力<br />\n<br />\n四樣都無的，唔該收皮。"},{"pid":"2bb25a09329d291552bc199769b968f3b4ef3904","tid":495791,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T06:26:17.000Z","msg":"繼續"},{"pid":"2cf7e258a4a0e5c924eeed38a3f9d1fd6fdbef62","tid":495791,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T06:41:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>正面情緒(+理性) : 哦, 唔緊要, \b再試第4個target , 相信之前果d 唔夾姐</blockquote><br />\n成個論證得兩個字「相信」，見唔到理性喺邊喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n理性係，知道「樣子」和「外表」的重要，更知道「衣著」和「打扮」的威力。努力學習如何變成「型男」。<br />\n<br />\n（打扮衣著可以勁到連性別和年齡都欺騙到，睇班cosplay偽娘就知。）"},{"pid":"6f121101f51ef699cb4e7187ca8145a7afda7848","tid":495791,"uid":100760,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T07:52:35.000Z","msg":"唔知真正嘅distribution，所以理性嘅estimate就係用observations去估真正嘅distribution，但當下嘅sample size唔夠多，最好收集多啲sample先去estimate<br />\n<br />\n呢個係我get到樓主想講嘅嘢"},{"pid":"2318994d1ab984f3a0828c9b5c1dab6935368ef4","tid":495791,"uid":82508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T08:15:03.000Z","msg":"睇返樓主d post 你成日諗野 一諗到一個位就會去到盡 鑽牛角尖 唔識多角度思考"},{"pid":"ca1d91a09c954b9bbcd6bf9ecacfeb23d6600dba","tid":495791,"uid":32483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T08:20:21.000Z","msg":"你好似唔係好知咩叫理性"},{"pid":"dfd4f99ab5d4ba240acfe7d67f7e315153136bc6","tid":495791,"uid":92117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T09:18:46.000Z","msg":"個例子fail，根本講緊個人情緒，感性<br />\n唔係全知又如何?<br />\n可以係有限資訊下做出最有利決策先叫理性<br />\n理性同感性要分開睇<br />\n因為兩者有時有衝突<br />\n但呢個情況更應該用理性解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"915aa83771949aca096032e5ff9b282ecc87f16a","tid":495791,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T10:13:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5871eacafb4a36cc85c8d55b471d07a4b6119324","tid":495791,"uid":86686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T10:15:41.000Z","msg":"樓主需要睇下李天命"}]}